1808 
1809 void CFlowOutput::SetCpInverseDesign(CSolver *solver, const CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config){
1810 
1811  /*--- Prepare to read the surface pressure files (CSV) ---*/
1812 
1813  const auto surfCp_filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName("TargetCp", curTimeIter, ".dat");
1814 
1815  /*--- Read the surface pressure file, on the first inner iteration. ---*/
1816 
1817  ifstream Surface_file;
1818  Surface_file.open(surfCp_filename);
1819 
1820  if (!Surface_file.good()) {
1821  solver->SetTotal_CpDiff(0.0);
1822  SetHistoryOutputValue("INVERSE_DESIGN_PRESSURE", 0.0);
1823  return;
1824  }
1825 
1826  if ((config->GetInnerIter() == 0) || config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) {
1827  string text_line;
1828  getline(Surface_file, text_line);
1829 
1830  while (getline(Surface_file, text_line)) {
1831  /*--- remove commas ---*/
1832  for (auto& c : text_line) if (c == ',') c = ' ';
1833  stringstream point_line(text_line);
1834 
1835  /*--- parse line ---*/
1836  unsigned long iPointGlobal;
1837  su2double XCoord, YCoord, ZCoord=0, Pressure, PressureCoeff;
1838 
1839  point_line >> iPointGlobal >> XCoord >> YCoord;
1840  if (nDim == 3) point_line >> ZCoord;
1841  point_line >> Pressure >> PressureCoeff;
1842 
1843  const auto iPoint = geometry->GetGlobal_to_Local_Point(iPointGlobal);
1844 
1845  /*--- If the point is on this rank set the Cp to associated vertices
1846  * (one point may be shared by multiple vertices). ---*/
1847  if (iPoint >= 0) {
1848  bool set = false;
1849  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); ++iMarker) {
1850  const auto iVertex = geometry->nodes->GetVertex(iPoint, iMarker);
1851 
1852  if (iVertex >= 0) {
1853  solver->SetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex, PressureCoeff);
1854  set = true;
1855  }
1856  }
1857  if (!set)
1858  cout << "WARNING: In file " << surfCp_filename << ", point " << iPointGlobal << " is not a vertex." << endl;
1859  }
1860  }
1861  }
1862 
1863  /*--- Compute the pressure difference. ---*/
1864 
1865  su2double PressDiff = 0.0;
1866 
1867  for (auto iMarker = 0u; iMarker < geometry->GetnMarker(); ++iMarker) {
1868 
1869  const auto Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
1870 
1871  if (config->GetSolid_Wall(iMarker) || (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
1872  for (auto iVertex = 0ul; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
1873 
1874  const auto iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1875  if (!geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) continue;
1876 
1877  const auto Cp = solver->GetCPressure(iMarker, iVertex);
1878  const auto CpTarget = solver->GetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex);
1879 
1880  const auto Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1881  const auto Area = GeometryToolbox::Norm(nDim, Normal);
1882 
1883  PressDiff += Area * pow(CpTarget-Cp, 2);
1884  }
1885  }
1886  }
1887  su2double tmp = PressDiff;
1888  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&tmp, &PressDiff, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1889 
1890  /*--- Update the total Cp difference coeffient. ---*/
1891 
1892  solver->SetTotal_CpDiff(PressDiff);
1893  SetHistoryOutputValue("INVERSE_DESIGN_PRESSURE", PressDiff);
1894 
1895 }
1896

1898 
1899  AddHistoryOutput("EQUIVALENT_AREA", "CEquiv_Area", ScreenOutputFormat::SCIENTIFIC, "EQUIVALENT_AREA", "Equivalent area", HistoryFieldType::COEFFICIENT);
1900 }
1901 
1902 void CFlowOutput::SetNearfieldInverseDesign(CSolver *solver, const CGeometry *geometry, const CConfig *config){
1903 
1904  ofstream EquivArea_file;
1905  su2double auxXCoord, auxYCoord, auxZCoord, InverseDesign = 0.0, DeltaX,
1906  Coord_i, Coord_j, jp1Coord, *Coord = nullptr, MeanFunction,
1907  *Face_Normal = nullptr, auxArea, auxPress, jFunction, jp1Function;
1908  unsigned long iPoint, auxPoint, auxDomain;
1909  ofstream NearFieldEA_file; ifstream TargetEA_file;
1910 
1911  const su2double XCoordBegin_OF = config->GetEA_IntLimit(0);
1912  const su2double XCoordEnd_OF = config->GetEA_IntLimit(1);
1913 
1914  const su2double AoA = -(config->GetAoA()*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
1915  const su2double EAScaleFactor = config->GetEA_ScaleFactor(); // The EA Obj. Func. should be ~ force based Obj. Func.
1916 
1917  const su2double Mach = config->GetMach();
1918  const su2double Gamma = config->GetGamma();
1919  const su2double Beta = sqrt(Mach*Mach-1.0);
1920  const su2double R_Plane = fabs(config->GetEA_IntLimit(2));
1921  const su2double Pressure_Inf = config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
1922 
1923  const su2double factor = 4.0*sqrt(2.0*Beta*R_Plane) / (Gamma*Pressure_Inf*Mach*Mach);
1924 
1925  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) cout << "Writing Equivalent Area files." << endl ;
1926 
1927  vector<unsigned long> Buffer_Receive_nVertex;
1928  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
1929  Buffer_Receive_nVertex.resize(size);
1930  }
1931 
1932  /*--- Compute the total number of points of the near-field ghost nodes ---*/
1933 
1934  unsigned long nLocalVertex_NearField = 0;
1935  for (unsigned short iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
1936  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)
1937  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
1938  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1939  Face_Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1940  Coord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1941 
1942  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))
1943  if ((Face_Normal[nDim-1] > 0.0) && (Coord[nDim-1] < 0.0))
1944  nLocalVertex_NearField ++;
1945  }
1946 
1947  /*--- Send Near-Field vertex information --*/
1948  unsigned long MaxLocalVertex_NearField, nVertex_NearField;
1949 
1950  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nLocalVertex_NearField, &nVertex_NearField, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1951  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nLocalVertex_NearField, &MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_MAX, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1952  SU2_MPI::Gather(&nLocalVertex_NearField, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Receive_nVertex.data(), 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
1953 
1954  vector<su2double> Buffer_Send_Xcoord (MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 0.0);
1955  vector<su2double> Buffer_Send_Ycoord (MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 0.0);
1956  vector<su2double> Buffer_Send_Zcoord (MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 0.0);
1957  vector<unsigned long> Buffer_Send_IdPoint (MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 0);
1958  vector<su2double> Buffer_Send_Pressure (MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 0.0);
1959  vector<su2double> Buffer_Send_FaceArea (MaxLocalVertex_NearField, 0.0);
1960 
1961  vector<su2double> Buffer_Receive_Xcoord;
1962  vector<su2double> Buffer_Receive_Ycoord;
1963  vector<su2double> Buffer_Receive_Zcoord;
1964  vector<unsigned long> Buffer_Receive_IdPoint;
1965  vector<su2double> Buffer_Receive_Pressure;
1966  vector<su2double> Buffer_Receive_FaceArea;
1967 
1968  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
1969  Buffer_Receive_Xcoord.resize(size*MaxLocalVertex_NearField);
1970  Buffer_Receive_Ycoord.resize(size*MaxLocalVertex_NearField);
1971  Buffer_Receive_Zcoord.resize(size*MaxLocalVertex_NearField);
1972  Buffer_Receive_IdPoint.resize(size*MaxLocalVertex_NearField);
1973  Buffer_Receive_Pressure.resize(size*MaxLocalVertex_NearField);
1974  Buffer_Receive_FaceArea.resize(size*MaxLocalVertex_NearField);
1975  }
1976 
1977  const auto nBuffer_Xcoord = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
1978  const auto nBuffer_Ycoord = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
1979  const auto nBuffer_Zcoord = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
1980  const auto nBuffer_IdPoint = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
1981  const auto nBuffer_Pressure = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
1982  const auto nBuffer_FaceArea = MaxLocalVertex_NearField;
1983 
1984 
1985  /*--- Copy coordinates, index points, and pressures to the auxiliar vector --*/
1986 
1987  nLocalVertex_NearField = 0;
1988  for (unsigned short iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++)
1989  if (config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker) == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)
1990  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
1991  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
1992  Face_Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
1993  Coord = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint);
1994 
1995  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint))
1996  if ((Face_Normal[nDim-1] > 0.0) && (Coord[nDim-1] < 0.0)) {
1997  Buffer_Send_IdPoint[nLocalVertex_NearField] = iPoint;
1998  Buffer_Send_Xcoord[nLocalVertex_NearField] = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 0);
1999  Buffer_Send_Ycoord[nLocalVertex_NearField] = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
2000  if (nDim == 3) {
2001  Buffer_Send_Zcoord[nLocalVertex_NearField] = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 2);
2002  }
2003  Buffer_Send_Pressure[nLocalVertex_NearField] = solver->GetNodes()->GetPressure(iPoint);
2004  Buffer_Send_FaceArea[nLocalVertex_NearField] = fabs(Face_Normal[nDim-1]);
2005  nLocalVertex_NearField++;
2006  }
2007  }
2008 
2009  /*--- Send all the information --*/
2010 
2011  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Xcoord.data(), nBuffer_Xcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Xcoord.data(), nBuffer_Xcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2012  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Ycoord.data(), nBuffer_Ycoord, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Ycoord.data(), nBuffer_Ycoord, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2013  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Zcoord.data(), nBuffer_Zcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Zcoord.data(), nBuffer_Zcoord, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2014  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_IdPoint.data(), nBuffer_IdPoint, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, Buffer_Receive_IdPoint.data(), nBuffer_IdPoint, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2015  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Pressure.data(), nBuffer_Pressure, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_Pressure.data(), nBuffer_Pressure, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2016  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_FaceArea.data(), nBuffer_FaceArea, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Receive_FaceArea.data(), nBuffer_FaceArea, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2017 
2018  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2019 
2020  vector<su2double> Xcoord(nVertex_NearField);
2021  vector<su2double> Ycoord(nVertex_NearField);
2022  vector<su2double> Zcoord(nVertex_NearField);
2023  vector<short> AzimuthalAngle(nVertex_NearField);
2024  vector<unsigned long> IdPoint(nVertex_NearField);
2025  vector<unsigned long> IdDomain(nVertex_NearField);
2026  vector<su2double> Pressure(nVertex_NearField);
2027  vector<su2double> FaceArea(nVertex_NearField);
2028  vector<su2double> EquivArea(nVertex_NearField);
2029  vector<su2double> TargetArea(nVertex_NearField);
2030  vector<su2double> NearFieldWeight(nVertex_NearField);
2031  vector<su2double> Weight(nVertex_NearField);
2032 
2033  nVertex_NearField = 0;
2034  for (int iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < size; iProcessor++) {
2035  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < Buffer_Receive_nVertex[iProcessor]; iVertex++) {
2036  Xcoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Xcoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
2037  Ycoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Ycoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
2038 
2039  if (nDim == 2) {
2040  AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 0;
2041  }
2042 
2043  if (nDim == 3) {
2044  Zcoord[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Zcoord[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
2045 
2046  /*--- Rotate the nearfield cylinder ---*/
2047 
2048  su2double YcoordRot = Ycoord[nVertex_NearField];
2049  su2double ZcoordRot = Xcoord[nVertex_NearField]*sin(AoA) + Zcoord[nVertex_NearField]*cos(AoA);
2050 
2051  /*--- Compute the Azimuthal angle ---*/
2052 
2053  su2double AngleDouble = fabs(atan(-YcoordRot/ZcoordRot)*180.0/PI_NUMBER);
2054 
2055  /*--- Fix an azimuthal line due to misalignments of the near-field ---*/
2056 
2057  su2double FixAzimuthalLine = config->GetFixAzimuthalLine();
2058 
2059  if ((AngleDouble >= FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1) && (AngleDouble <= FixAzimuthalLine + 0.1))
2060  AngleDouble = FixAzimuthalLine - 0.1;
2061 
2062  const auto AngleInt = SU2_TYPE::Short(floor(AngleDouble + 0.5));
2063 
2064  if (AngleInt >= 0) AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = AngleInt;
2065  else AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] = 180 + AngleInt;
2066  }
2067 
2068  if (AzimuthalAngle[nVertex_NearField] <= 60) {
2069  IdPoint[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_IdPoint[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
2070  Pressure[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_Pressure[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
2071  FaceArea[nVertex_NearField] = Buffer_Receive_FaceArea[iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_NearField+iVertex];
2072  IdDomain[nVertex_NearField] = iProcessor;
2073  nVertex_NearField++;
2074  }
2075  }
2076  }
2077 
2078 
2079  vector<short> PhiAngleList;
2080  vector<short>::iterator IterPhiAngleList;
2081 
2082  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex_NearField; iVertex++)
2083  PhiAngleList.push_back(AzimuthalAngle[iVertex]);
2084 
2085  sort( PhiAngleList.begin(), PhiAngleList.end());
2086  IterPhiAngleList = unique( PhiAngleList.begin(), PhiAngleList.end());
2087  PhiAngleList.resize( IterPhiAngleList - PhiAngleList.begin() );
2088 
2089  /*--- Create vectors and distribute the values among the different PhiAngle queues ---*/
2090 
2091  vector<vector<su2double> > Xcoord_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2092  vector<vector<su2double> > Ycoord_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2093  vector<vector<su2double> > Zcoord_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2094  vector<vector<unsigned long> > IdPoint_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2095  vector<vector<unsigned long> > IdDomain_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2096  vector<vector<su2double> > Pressure_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2097  vector<vector<su2double> > FaceArea_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2098  vector<vector<su2double> > EquivArea_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2099  vector<vector<su2double> > TargetArea_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2100  vector<vector<su2double> > NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2101  vector<vector<su2double> > Weight_PhiAngle(PhiAngleList.size());
2102 
2103  /*--- Distribute the values among the different PhiAngles ---*/
2104 
2105  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < nVertex_NearField; iVertex++)
2106  for (unsigned short iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
2107  if (AzimuthalAngle[iVertex] == PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle]) {
2108  Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Xcoord[iVertex]);
2109  Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Ycoord[iVertex]);
2110  Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Zcoord[iVertex]);
2111  IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(IdPoint[iVertex]);
2112  IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(IdDomain[iVertex]);
2113  Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Pressure[iVertex]);
2114  FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(FaceArea[iVertex]);
2115  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(EquivArea[iVertex]);
2116  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(TargetArea[iVertex]);
2117  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(NearFieldWeight[iVertex]);
2118  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].push_back(Weight[iVertex]);
2119  }
2120 
2121  /*--- Order the arrays (x Coordinate, Pressure, Point, and Domain) ---*/
2122 
2123  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
2124  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
2125  for (unsigned long jVertex = 0; jVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size() - 1 - iVertex; jVertex++)
2126  if (Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] > Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]) {
2127  auxXCoord = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxXCoord;
2128  auxYCoord = Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Ycoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxYCoord;
2129  auxZCoord = Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxZCoord;
2130  auxPress = Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxPress;
2131  auxArea = FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; FaceArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxArea;
2132  auxPoint = IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; IdPoint_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxPoint;
2133  auxDomain = IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]; IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] = IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]; IdDomain_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] = auxDomain;
2134  }
2135 
2136 
2137  /*--- Check that all the azimuth lists have the same size ---*/
2138 
2139  auto nVertex = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0].size();
2140  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
2141  auto nVertex_aux = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size();
2142  if (nVertex_aux != nVertex) cout <<"Be careful! One azimuth list is shorter than the other.\n";
2143  nVertex = min(nVertex, nVertex_aux);
2144  }
2145 
2146  /*--- Compute equivalent area distribution at each azimuth angle ---*/
2147 
2148  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
2149  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][0] = 0.0;
2150  for (unsigned long iVertex = 1; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
2151  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
2152 
2153  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
2154 
2155  for (unsigned long jVertex = 0; jVertex < iVertex-1; jVertex++) {
2156 
2157  Coord_j = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]*sin(AoA);
2158  jp1Coord = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1]*sin(AoA);
2159 
2160  jFunction = factor*(Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex] - Pressure_Inf)*sqrt(Coord_i-Coord_j);
2161  jp1Function = factor*(Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex+1] - Pressure_Inf)*sqrt(Coord_i-jp1Coord);
2162 
2163  DeltaX = (jp1Coord-Coord_j);
2164  MeanFunction = 0.5*(jp1Function + jFunction);
2165  EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] += DeltaX * MeanFunction;
2166  }
2167  }
2168  }
2169 
2170  /*--- Create a file with the equivalent area distribution at each azimuthal angle ---*/
2171 
2172  NearFieldEA_file.precision(config->GetOutput_Precision());
2173 
2174  NearFieldEA_file.open("Equivalent_Area.dat", ios::out);
2175  NearFieldEA_file << "TITLE = \"Equivalent Area evaluation at each azimuthal angle\"" << "\n";
2176 
2177  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
2178  NearFieldEA_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (in) at r="<< R_Plane*12.0 << " in. (cyl. coord. system)\"";
2179  else
2180  NearFieldEA_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (m) at r="<< R_Plane << " m. (cylindrical coordinate system)\"";
2181 
2182  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
2183  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
2184  NearFieldEA_file << ", \"Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>), <greek>F</greek>= " << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"";
2185  else
2186  NearFieldEA_file << ", \"Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>), <greek>F</greek>= " << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"";
2187  }
2188 
2189  NearFieldEA_file << "\n";
2190  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[0].size(); iVertex++) {
2191 
2192  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
2193  su2double XcoordRot_init = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*sin(AoA);
2194 
2195  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
2196  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init) * 12.0;
2197  else
2198  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init);
2199 
2200  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
2201  NearFieldEA_file << scientific << ", " << EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
2202  }
2203 
2204  NearFieldEA_file << "\n";
2205 
2206  }
2207  NearFieldEA_file.close();
2208 
2209 
2210  /*--- Read target equivalent area from the configuration file,
2211  this first implementation requires a complete table (same as the original
2212  EA table). so... no interpolation. ---*/
2213 
2214  vector<vector<su2double> > TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans;
2215  TargetEA_file.open("TargetEA.dat", ios::in);
2216 
2217  if (TargetEA_file.fail()) {
2218  /*--- Set the table to 0 ---*/
2219  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
2220  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
2221  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
2222  }
2223  else {
2224 
2225  /*--- skip header lines ---*/
2226 
2227  string line;
2228  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
2229  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
2230 
2231  while (TargetEA_file) {
2232 
2233  string line;
2234  getline(TargetEA_file, line);
2235  istringstream is(line);
2236  vector<su2double> row;
2237  unsigned short iter = 0;
2238 
2239  while (is.good()) {
2240  string token;
2241  getline(is, token,',');
2242 
2243  istringstream js(token);
2244 
2245  su2double data;
2246  js >> data;
2247 
2248  /*--- The first element in the table is the coordinate (in or m)---*/
2249 
2250  if (iter != 0) row.push_back(data);
2251  iter++;
2252 
2253  }
2254  TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans.push_back(row);
2255  }
2256 
2257  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
2258  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++)
2259  TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = TargetArea_PhiAngle_Trans[iVertex][iPhiAngle];
2260 
2261  }
2262 
2263  /*--- Divide by the number of Phi angles in the nearfield ---*/
2264 
2265  su2double PhiFactor = 1.0/su2double(PhiAngleList.size());
2266 
2267  /*--- Evaluate the objective function ---*/
2268 
2269  InverseDesign = 0;
2270  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++)
2271  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
2272  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 1.0;
2273  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
2274 
2275  su2double Difference = EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]-TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
2276  su2double percentage = fabs(Difference)*100/fabs(TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]);
2277 
2278  if ((percentage < 0.1) || (Coord_i < XCoordBegin_OF) || (Coord_i > XCoordEnd_OF)) Difference = 0.0;
2279 
2280  InverseDesign += EAScaleFactor*PhiFactor*Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*Difference*Difference;
2281  }
2282 
2283  /*--- Evaluate the weight of the nearfield pressure (adjoint input) ---*/
2284 
2285  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
2286  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
2287  Coord_i = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex];
2288  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 0.0;
2289  for (unsigned long jVertex = iVertex; jVertex < EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); jVertex++) {
2290  Coord_j = Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex];
2291  Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] = 1.0;
2292 
2293  su2double Difference = EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]-TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex];
2294  su2double percentage = fabs(Difference)*100/fabs(TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][jVertex]);
2295 
2296  if ((percentage < 0.1) || (Coord_j < XCoordBegin_OF) || (Coord_j > XCoordEnd_OF)) Difference = 0.0;
2297 
2298  NearFieldWeight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] += EAScaleFactor*PhiFactor*Weight_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]*2.0*Difference*factor*sqrt(Coord_j-Coord_i);
2299  }
2300  }
2301  }
2302 
2303  /*--- Write the Nearfield pressure at each Azimuthal PhiAngle ---*/
2304 
2305  EquivArea_file.precision(config->GetOutput_Precision());
2306 
2307  EquivArea_file.open("nearfield_flow.dat", ios::out);
2308  EquivArea_file << "TITLE = \"Equivalent Area evaluation at each azimuthal angle\"" << "\n";
2309 
2310  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
2311  EquivArea_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (in) at r="<< R_Plane*12.0 << " in. (cyl. coord. system)\",\"Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Target Equivalent Area (ft<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
2312  else
2313  EquivArea_file << "VARIABLES = \"Height (m) at r="<< R_Plane << " m. (cylindrical coordinate system)\",\"Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Target Equivalent Area (m<sup>2</sup>)\",\"Cp\"" << "\n";
2314 
2315  for (unsigned long iPhiAngle = 0; iPhiAngle < PhiAngleList.size(); iPhiAngle++) {
2316  EquivArea_file << fixed << "ZONE T= \"<greek>F</greek>=" << PhiAngleList[iPhiAngle] << " deg.\"" << "\n";
2317  for (unsigned long iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle].size(); iVertex++) {
2318 
2319  su2double XcoordRot = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][iVertex]*sin(AoA);
2320  su2double XcoordRot_init = Xcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*cos(AoA) - Zcoord_PhiAngle[0][0]*sin(AoA);
2321 
2322  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US)
2323  EquivArea_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init) * 12.0;
2324  else
2325  EquivArea_file << scientific << (XcoordRot - XcoordRot_init);
2326 
2327  EquivArea_file << scientific << ", " << EquivArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]
2328  << ", " << TargetArea_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex] << ", " << (Pressure_PhiAngle[iPhiAngle][iVertex]-Pressure_Inf)/Pressure_Inf << "\n";
2329  }
2330  }
2331 
2332  EquivArea_file.close();
2333 
2334  }
2335 
2336  /*--- Send the value of the NearField coefficient to all the processors ---*/
2337 
2338  SU2_MPI::Bcast(&InverseDesign, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
2339 
2340  /*--- Store the value of the NearField coefficient ---*/
2341 
2342  solver->SetTotal_CEquivArea(InverseDesign);
2343  SetHistoryOutputValue("EQUIVALENT_AREA", InverseDesign);
2344 
2345 }

2360 void CFlowOutput::WriteMetaData(const CConfig *config){
2361 
2362  ofstream meta_file;
2363 
2364  string filename = "flow";
2365 
2366  filename = config->GetFilename(filename, ".meta", curTimeIter);
2367 
2368  /*--- All processors open the file. ---*/
2369 
2370  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
2371  cout << "Writing Flow Meta-Data file: " << filename << endl;
2372 
2373  meta_file.open(filename.c_str(), ios::out);
2374  meta_file.precision(15);
2375 
2376  if (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST || config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND)
2377  meta_file <<"ITER= " << curTimeIter + 1 << endl;
2378  else
2379  meta_file <<"ITER= " << curInnerIter + config->GetExtIter_OffSet() + 1 << endl;
2380 
2381  if (config->GetFixed_CL_Mode()){
2382  meta_file <<"AOA= " << config->GetAoA() - config->GetAoA_Offset() << endl;
2383  meta_file <<"SIDESLIP_ANGLE= " << config->GetAoS() - config->GetAoS_Offset() << endl;
2384  meta_file <<"DCD_DCL_VALUE= " << config->GetdCD_dCL() << endl;
2385  if (nDim==3){
2386  meta_file <<"DCMX_DCL_VALUE= " << config->GetdCMx_dCL() << endl;
2387  meta_file <<"DCMY_DCL_VALUE= " << config->GetdCMy_dCL() << endl;
2388  }
2389  meta_file <<"DCMZ_DCL_VALUE= " << config->GetdCMz_dCL() << endl;
2390  }
2391  meta_file <<"INITIAL_BCTHRUST= " << config->GetInitial_BCThrust() << endl;
2392 
2393 
2394  if (( config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_EULER ||
2395  config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES ||
2396  config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_RANS )) {
2397  meta_file << "SENS_AOA=" << GetHistoryFieldValue("SENS_AOA") * PI_NUMBER / 180.0 << endl;
2398  }
2399 
2400  if(config->GetKind_Streamwise_Periodic() == ENUM_STREAMWISE_PERIODIC::MASSFLOW) {
2401  meta_file << "STREAMWISE_PERIODIC_PRESSURE_DROP=" << GetHistoryFieldValue("STREAMWISE_DP") << endl;
2402  }
2403  }
2404 
2405  meta_file.close();
2406 }

2408 void CFlowOutput::WriteForcesBreakdown(const CConfig* config, const CSolver* flow_solver) const {
2409  // clang-format off
2410  if (rank != MASTER_NODE) return;
2411 
2412  const bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE);
2413  const bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE);
2414  const bool unsteady = config->GetTime_Domain();
2415  const bool viscous = config->GetViscous();
2416  const bool dynamic_grid = config->GetDynamic_Grid();
2417  const bool gravity = config->GetGravityForce();
2418  const TURB_MODEL Kind_Turb_Model = config->GetKind_Turb_Model();
2419  const bool turbulent = Kind_Turb_Model != TURB_MODEL::NONE;
2420  const TURB_TRANS_MODEL Kind_Trans_Model = config->GetKind_Trans_Model();
2421  const bool transition = Kind_Trans_Model != TURB_TRANS_MODEL::NONE;
2422  const bool fixed_cl = config->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
2423  const auto Kind_Solver = config->GetKind_Solver();
2424  const auto Ref_NonDim = config->GetRef_NonDim();
2425  const auto nMonitoring = config->GetnMarker_Monitoring();
2426 
2427  auto fileName = config->GetBreakdown_FileName();
2428  if (unsteady) {
2429  const auto lastindex = fileName.find_last_of('.');
2430  const auto ext = fileName.substr(lastindex, fileName.size());
2431  fileName = fileName.substr(0, lastindex);
2432  fileName = config->GetFilename(fileName, ext, curTimeIter);
2433  }
2434 
2435  /*--- Output the mean flow solution using only the master node ---*/
2436 
2437  cout << "\nWriting the forces breakdown file (" << fileName << ")." << endl;
2438 
2439  vector<su2double> Surface_CL(nMonitoring);
2440  vector<su2double> Surface_CD(nMonitoring);
2441  vector<su2double> Surface_CSF(nMonitoring);
2442  vector<su2double> Surface_CEff(nMonitoring);
2443  vector<su2double> Surface_CFx(nMonitoring);
2444  vector<su2double> Surface_CFy(nMonitoring);
2445  vector<su2double> Surface_CFz(nMonitoring);
2446  vector<su2double> Surface_CMx(nMonitoring);
2447  vector<su2double> Surface_CMy(nMonitoring);
2448  vector<su2double> Surface_CMz(nMonitoring);
2449 
2450  vector<su2double> Surface_CL_Inv(nMonitoring);
2451  vector<su2double> Surface_CD_Inv(nMonitoring);
2452  vector<su2double> Surface_CSF_Inv(nMonitoring);
2453  vector<su2double> Surface_CEff_Inv(nMonitoring);
2454  vector<su2double> Surface_CFx_Inv(nMonitoring);
2455  vector<su2double> Surface_CFy_Inv(nMonitoring);
2456  vector<su2double> Surface_CFz_Inv(nMonitoring);
2457  vector<su2double> Surface_CMx_Inv(nMonitoring);
2458  vector<su2double> Surface_CMy_Inv(nMonitoring);
2459  vector<su2double> Surface_CMz_Inv(nMonitoring);
2460 
2461  vector<su2double> Surface_CL_Visc(nMonitoring);
2462  vector<su2double> Surface_CD_Visc(nMonitoring);
2463  vector<su2double> Surface_CSF_Visc(nMonitoring);
2464  vector<su2double> Surface_CEff_Visc(nMonitoring);
2465  vector<su2double> Surface_CFx_Visc(nMonitoring);
2466  vector<su2double> Surface_CFy_Visc(nMonitoring);
2467  vector<su2double> Surface_CFz_Visc(nMonitoring);
2468  vector<su2double> Surface_CMx_Visc(nMonitoring);
2469  vector<su2double> Surface_CMy_Visc(nMonitoring);
2470  vector<su2double> Surface_CMz_Visc(nMonitoring);
2471 
2472  vector<su2double> Surface_CL_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2473  vector<su2double> Surface_CD_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2474  vector<su2double> Surface_CSF_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2475  vector<su2double> Surface_CEff_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2476  vector<su2double> Surface_CFx_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2477  vector<su2double> Surface_CFy_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2478  vector<su2double> Surface_CFz_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2479  vector<su2double> Surface_CMx_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2480  vector<su2double> Surface_CMy_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2481  vector<su2double> Surface_CMz_Mnt(nMonitoring);
2482 
2483  /*--- Flow solution coefficients ---*/
2484 
2485  const auto Total_CL = flow_solver->GetTotal_CL();
2486  const auto Total_CD = flow_solver->GetTotal_CD();
2487  const auto Total_CSF = flow_solver->GetTotal_CSF();
2488  const auto Total_CEff = flow_solver->GetTotal_CEff();
2489  const auto Total_CMx = flow_solver->GetTotal_CMx();
2490  const auto Total_CMy = flow_solver->GetTotal_CMy();
2491  const auto Total_CMz = flow_solver->GetTotal_CMz();
2492  const auto Total_CFx = flow_solver->GetTotal_CFx();
2493  const auto Total_CFy = flow_solver->GetTotal_CFy();
2494  const auto Total_CFz = flow_solver->GetTotal_CFz();
2495 
2496  su2double Total_CoPx = 0.0, Total_CoPy = 0.0, Total_CoPz = 0.0;
2497  if (nDim == 2) {
2498  Total_CoPx = flow_solver->GetTotal_CoPx() / flow_solver->GetTotal_CFy();
2499  Total_CoPy = flow_solver->GetTotal_CoPy() / flow_solver->GetTotal_CFx();
2500  } else {
2501  Total_CoPx = flow_solver->GetTotal_CoPx() / flow_solver->GetTotal_CFz();
2502  Total_CoPz = flow_solver->GetTotal_CoPz() / flow_solver->GetTotal_CFx();
2503  }
2504  if (us_units) {
2505  Total_CoPx *= 12.0;
2506  Total_CoPy *= 12.0;
2507  Total_CoPz *= 12.0;
2508  }
2509 
2510  /*--- Flow inviscid solution coefficients ---*/
2511 
2512  const auto Inv_CL = flow_solver->GetAllBound_CL_Inv();
2513  const auto Inv_CD = flow_solver->GetAllBound_CD_Inv();
2514  const auto Inv_CSF = flow_solver->GetAllBound_CSF_Inv();
2515  const auto Inv_CEff = flow_solver->GetAllBound_CEff_Inv();
2516  const auto Inv_CMx = flow_solver->GetAllBound_CMx_Inv();

3917 
3918 bool CFlowOutput::WriteVolumeOutput(CConfig *config, unsigned long Iter, bool force_writing, unsigned short iFile){
3919 
3920  bool writeRestart = false;
3921  auto FileFormat = config->GetVolumeOutputFiles();
3922 
3923  if (config->GetTime_Domain()){
3924  if (((config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST) || (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::TIME_STEPPING)) &&
3925  ((Iter == 0) || (Iter % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0))){
3926  return true;
3927  }
3928 
3929  /* check if we want to write a restart file*/
3930  if (FileFormat[iFile] == OUTPUT_TYPE::RESTART_ASCII || FileFormat[iFile] == OUTPUT_TYPE::RESTART_BINARY || FileFormat[iFile] == OUTPUT_TYPE::CSV) {
3931  writeRestart = true;
3932  }
3933 
3934  /* only write 'double' files for the restart files */
3935  if ((config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND) &&
3936  ((Iter == 0) || (Iter % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0) ||
3937  (((Iter+1) % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0) && writeRestart) || // Restarts need 2 old solutions.
3938  (((Iter+2) == config->GetnTime_Iter()) && writeRestart))){ // The last timestep is written anyway but one needs the step before for restarts.
3939  return true;
3940  }
3941  } else {
3942  if (config->GetFixed_CL_Mode() && config->GetFinite_Difference_Mode()) return false;
3943  return ((Iter > 0) && Iter % config->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(iFile) == 0) || force_writing;
3944  }
3945 
3946  return force_writing;
3947 }
3948 
3949 void CFlowOutput::SetTimeAveragedFields() {
3950  AddVolumeOutput("MEAN_DENSITY", "MeanDensity", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean density");
3951  AddVolumeOutput("MEAN_VELOCITY-X", "MeanVelocity_x", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean velocity x-component");
3952  AddVolumeOutput("MEAN_VELOCITY-Y", "MeanVelocity_y", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean velocity y-component");
3953  if (nDim == 3)
3954  AddVolumeOutput("MEAN_VELOCITY-Z", "MeanVelocity_z", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean velocity z-component");
3955 
3956  AddVolumeOutput("MEAN_PRESSURE", "MeanPressure", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean pressure");
3957  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_U", "RMS[u]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS u");
3958  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_V", "RMS[v]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS v");
3959  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_UV", "RMS[uv]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS uv");
3960  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_P", "RMS[Pressure]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS Pressure");
3961  AddVolumeOutput("UUPRIME", "u'u'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean Reynolds-stress component u'u'");
3962  AddVolumeOutput("VVPRIME", "v'v'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean Reynolds-stress component v'v'");
3963  AddVolumeOutput("UVPRIME", "u'v'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean Reynolds-stress component u'v'");
3964  AddVolumeOutput("PPRIME", "p'p'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean pressure fluctuation p'p'");
3965  if (nDim == 3){
3966  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_W", "RMS[w]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS u");
3967  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_UW", "RMS[uw]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS uw");
3968  AddVolumeOutput("RMS_VW", "RMS[vw]", "TIME_AVERAGE", "RMS vw");
3969  AddVolumeOutput("WWPRIME", "w'w'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean Reynolds-stress component w'w'");
3970  AddVolumeOutput("UWPRIME", "w'u'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean Reynolds-stress component w'u'");
3971  AddVolumeOutput("VWPRIME", "w'v'", "TIME_AVERAGE", "Mean Reynolds-stress component w'v'");
3972  }

3975 void CFlowOutput::LoadTimeAveragedData(unsigned long iPoint, const CVariable *Node_Flow){
3976  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_DENSITY", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetDensity(iPoint));
3977  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-X", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0));
3978  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Y", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1));
3979  if (nDim == 3)
3980  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Z", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2));
3981 
3982  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_PRESSURE", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetPressure(iPoint));
3983 
3984  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_U", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0),2));
3985  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_V", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1),2));
3986  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UV", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0) * Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1));
3987  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_P", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetPressure(iPoint),2));
3988  if (nDim == 3){
3989  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_W", iPoint, pow(Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2),2));
3990  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_VW", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2) * Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,1));
3991  SetAvgVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UW", iPoint, Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,2) * Node_Flow->GetVelocity(iPoint,0));
3992  }
3993 
3994  const su2double umean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-X", iPoint);
3995  const su2double uumean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_U", iPoint);
3996  const su2double vmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Y", iPoint);
3997  const su2double vvmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_V", iPoint);
3998  const su2double uvmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UV", iPoint);
3999  const su2double pmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_PRESSURE", iPoint);
4000  const su2double ppmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_P", iPoint);
4001 
4002  SetVolumeOutputValue("UUPRIME", iPoint, -(umean*umean - uumean));
4003  SetVolumeOutputValue("VVPRIME", iPoint, -(vmean*vmean - vvmean));
4004  SetVolumeOutputValue("UVPRIME", iPoint, -(umean*vmean - uvmean));
4005  SetVolumeOutputValue("PPRIME", iPoint, -(pmean*pmean - ppmean));
4006  if (nDim == 3){
4007  const su2double wmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("MEAN_VELOCITY-Z", iPoint);
4008  const su2double wwmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_W", iPoint);
4009  const su2double uwmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_UW", iPoint);
4010  const su2double vwmean = GetVolumeOutputValue("RMS_VW", iPoint);
4011  SetVolumeOutputValue("WWPRIME", iPoint, -(wmean*wmean - wwmean));
4012  SetVolumeOutputValue("UWPRIME", iPoint, -(umean*wmean - uwmean));
4013  SetVolumeOutputValue("VWPRIME", iPoint, -(vmean*wmean - vwmean));
4014  }
4015 }

4017 void CFlowOutput::SetFixedCLScreenOutput(const CConfig *config){
4018  PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter FixedCLSummary(&cout);
4019 
4020  if (fabs(historyOutput_Map["CL_DRIVER_COMMAND"].value) > 1e-16){
4021  FixedCLSummary.AddColumn("Fixed CL Mode", 40);
4022  FixedCLSummary.AddColumn("Value", 30);
4023  FixedCLSummary.SetAlign(PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter::LEFT);
4024  FixedCLSummary.PrintHeader();
4025  FixedCLSummary << "Current CL" << historyOutput_Map["LIFT"].value;
4026  FixedCLSummary << "Target CL" << config->GetTarget_CL();
4027  FixedCLSummary << "Previous AOA" << historyOutput_Map["PREV_AOA"].value;
4028  if (config->GetFinite_Difference_Mode()){
4029  FixedCLSummary << "Changed AoA by (Finite Difference step)" << historyOutput_Map["CL_DRIVER_COMMAND"].value;
4030  lastInnerIter = curInnerIter - 1;
4031  }
4032  else
4033  FixedCLSummary << "Changed AoA by" << historyOutput_Map["CL_DRIVER_COMMAND"].value;
4034  FixedCLSummary.PrintFooter();
4035  SetScreenHeader(config);
4036  }
4037 
4038  else if (config->GetFinite_Difference_Mode() && historyOutput_Map["AOA"].value == historyOutput_Map["PREV_AOA"].value){
4039  FixedCLSummary.AddColumn("Fixed CL Mode (Finite Difference)", 40);
4040  FixedCLSummary.AddColumn("Value", 30);
4041  FixedCLSummary.SetAlign(PrintingToolbox::CTablePrinter::LEFT);
4042  FixedCLSummary.PrintHeader();
4043  FixedCLSummary << "Delta CL / Delta AoA" << config->GetdCL_dAlpha();
4044  FixedCLSummary << "Delta CD / Delta CL" << config->GetdCD_dCL();
4045  if (nDim == 3){
4046  FixedCLSummary << "Delta CMx / Delta CL" << config->GetdCMx_dCL();
4047  FixedCLSummary << "Delta CMy / Delta CL" << config->GetdCMy_dCL();
4048  }
4049  FixedCLSummary << "Delta CMz / Delta CL" << config->GetdCMz_dCL();
4050  FixedCLSummary.PrintFooter();
4051  curInnerIter = lastInnerIter;
4052  WriteMetaData(config);
4053  curInnerIter = config->GetInnerIter();
4054  }
4055 }
